        "created_at": "2025-07-15T16:36:04.318Z",
        "cooked": "<p>It is not technically possible since the ‚Äúdisappearing messages‚Äù timer can be changed after the invitation but before accepting the invitation.</p>\n<p>I also caution you to not treat ‚Äúdisappearing messages‚Äù as a privacy enhancing feature despite its inclusion in the privacy section of the settings.</p>",
